            ul.mb-4
              li <strong>1-3:</strong> Routine work with templates (login forms, standard bug fixes)
              li <strong>4-6:</strong> Similar work needing adaptation (new payment provider, different framework)
              li <strong>7-10:</strong> New territory requiring R&D (first ML model, blockchain integration)
            
            p.small.text-muted.mb-4 Ask: "How much Googling vs. copy-pasting from previous work?"
            
            h3.h5.mb-3.
              <strong>Scope:</strong> How big is the work?
            
            ul.mb-4
              li <strong>1-3:</strong> Small, isolated change (button color, single validation)
              li <strong>4-6:</strong> Multiple components (dashboard page, API + form)
              li <strong>7-10:</strong> System-wide changes (database migration, entire microservice)
            
            p.small.text-muted.mb-4 Ask: "How many files/systems will we touch?"
            
            h3.h5.mb-3.
              <strong>People:</strong> Coordination complexity?
            
            ul.mb-4
